---
import ThankYouLayout from '../../layouts/ThankYouLayout.astro';
---

<ThankYouLayout
  productSlug="level-6-governance-toolkit"
  description="Your Level 6 Governance Toolkit is ready to download."
  readyLine="Your Level 6 Governance Toolkit is ready."
  downloadHeading="Download your toolkit"
  downloadHref="/downloads/Ostrom-Score-Self-Assessment-Kit-v1.0.pdf"
  downloadCtaLabel="Download the toolkit"
>
  <Fragment slot="download-description">
    <p>Three instruments. One 60-point scorecard. The Ostrom Score measures commons health. The Identity Violation Assessment measures entity integrity. The Agent Consent Architecture measures participation. The Synthesis Guide ties them together.</p>
  </Fragment>

  <Fragment slot="next-steps">
    <a href="/products/ostrom-score" class="pd-upsell-card">
      <h3>Start with Ostrom</h3>
      <p>The Ostrom Score is the most accessible instrument and surfaces urgency fastest. Begin there.</p>
      <span class="pd-upsell-link">Ostrom Score &rarr;</span>
    </a>
    <a href="/products/identity-violation-assessment" class="pd-upsell-card">
      <h3>Then Identity</h3>
      <p>The Identity Violation Assessment reveals whether the entities in your commons are genuine.</p>
      <span class="pd-upsell-link">Identity Violation &rarr;</span>
    </a>
    <a href="/products/agent-consent-architecture" class="pd-upsell-card">
      <h3>Then Consent</h3>
      <p>The Agent Consent Architecture evaluates whether entities can participate in their own governance.</p>
      <span class="pd-upsell-link">Agent Consent &rarr;</span>
    </a>
    <a href="/products/level-6-governance-toolkit" class="pd-upsell-card">
      <h3>Combine with The Gap</h3>
      <p>Use the Synthesis Guide to calculate your combined 60-point score and identify your highest-priority gap.</p>
      <span class="pd-upsell-link">Toolkit page &rarr;</span>
    </a>
  </Fragment>
</ThankYouLayout>
